title: Aha-Soft Icon Software Collection Portable 23.7.2016 / Icon Pack
description:
Aha-Soft Icon Software Collection Portable July 2016 + Icon Pack

Aha-Soft delivers icon and graphic applications that are user-friendly.. The company has developed graphic software products and stock icon sets specifically designed to minimize the time authors spend creating icons, cursors and small images.	

These portable applications were created with VMWare ThinApp, compatible with any Windows version (XP and above, 32/64-bit). All applications are registered, shell extensions and file associations are disabled.

Just extract the archive and run one of these application.

AhaView
is a handy image viewer and converter. It allows you to browse, view, organize and convert your digital images.

Any to Icon
allows you to convert multiple BMP, JPEG, GIF, PNG, PSD and WMF images to icons in one action. It also breaks down entire icon libraries into individual icons.

ArtCursors
allows you to find, create, edit, import and export cursors and manage cursor libraries. It supports static and animated cursors.

ArtIcons Pro
is an advanced icon-specific utility for Windows. It supports GIF, PSD, RC, XPM, XBM, WBMP, CUR, ANI formats in addition to standard versions. 

Icon to Any
is an icon converter for Windows. Icon to Any allows you to convert Windows icons, cursors and Mac OS icons into ICO, ICNS, CUR, BMP, JPEG, GIF, PNG, PSD, TIFF, XBM, XPM, WBMP and RC files.

IconLover
is a complete icon and cursor solution. Use it to edit, convert, import and export icons, cursors and other tiny images as well as manage icon collections and image lists. 

IconXP
edits Windows icons in color depths up to 32-bit True Color. Import and export ICO, BMP, GIF, JPEG, PNG, CUR, ANI, PSD, WMF formats. Apply drop shadow, smooth, roll effects
